[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0041","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0041.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0387","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/98 遗留凭据缓存信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows 95和Windows 98系统中存在一个从Windows for Workgroups继承的遗留凭据缓存机制，该机制会在RAM中以明文形式缓存网络登录凭据。虽然该机制在Windows 95/98中已不再使用，但代码仍被保留。攻击者若拥有物理访问权限且系统自上次网络会话后未重启，可通过查询该缓存获取上一个网络用户的明文密码，导致敏感凭据泄露。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0387"],"sources":["cve","ms"],"published":"1999-11-29","updated":"1999-11-29","remediation":"微软已发布安全公告MS99-052修复此漏洞。Windows 95用户应安装KB168115更新补丁，Windows 98用户应安装对应安全更新。Windows 98第二版不受此漏洞影响。建议用户及时安装补丁并限制物理访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T12:25:41.557377081+00:00","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ168115","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/829","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-052"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0041.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0625","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0625.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0839","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 任务计划程序权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 系统中，Internet Explorer 5 的脱机浏览包所安装的任务计划程序（Task Scheduler）存在权限提升漏洞。该任务计划程序替代了原生 NT 计划服务，但未对 AT 作业进行数字签名验证。具有本地登录权限的普通用户若能获得管理员所拥有文件的更改权限，可将该文件修改为恶意的 AT 作业并放入计划任务目录，从而绕过访问控制机制，以 System 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 IE 5 的 Windows NT 4.0 系统（需安装脱机浏览包），CVSS v2.0 评分 7.2，危害等级高。微软已在 IE 5.01 版本中通过数字签名机制修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0839"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-29","updated":"1999-11-29","remediation":"建议立即升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.01 或更高版本，该版本在 AT 作业创建时进行数字签名并执行时验证签名，防止非授权修改。如无法升级，可卸载 IE 5 Offline Browsing Pack 并改用 Windows NT 原生计划任务服务（AT 服务）替代，同时在安全策略中限制普通用户的交互式登录权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0625.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0023","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0023.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0317","title":"Linux su 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linux su 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 su 程序传递特制的长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而将普通用户权限提升至 root 超级管理员权限。该漏洞影响早期 Linux 内核版本中的 su 组件，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用，一旦成功可完全控制目标系统，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0317"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-11-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.383","remediation":"立即升级 shadow-utils（shadow）软件包至最新版本，所有现代 Linux 发行版均已修复此漏洞。Red Hat 系执行 `yum update shadow-utils`，Debian 系执行 `apt-get update && apt-get install --only-upgrade shadow`。如无法升级，限制非授权用户的本地 shell 访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0317"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0023.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0643","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0643.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0845","title":"SCO Unixware su 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SCO Unixware 操作系统中 su 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 su 命令提交超长用户名参数，触发栈缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 SCO Unixware 2.1、7.0、7.0.1、7.1 及 7.1.1 等多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。利用前提是攻击者拥有本地系统访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0845"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-25","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 SCO Unixware 至厂商已发布补丁的最新版本（如 7.1.1 以上），或应用 SCO 官方安全补丁 SSE018。对于已停止维护的系统，建议移除 su 程序的 setuid root 权限（chmod u-s /bin/su）作为临时缓解，并尽快迁移至受支持的操作系统平台以避免持续暴露于未修复漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0845","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19643"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0643.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0989","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0989.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1163","title":"HP 800系列S/X/V类服务器服务支持处理器测试站远程未授权访问漏洞","description":"HP Series 800 S/X/V 类服务器的服务支持处理器（SSP）Teststation 存在未授权访问漏洞。远程攻击者无需任何身份认证即可通过网络连接 SSP Teststation 功能模块，该模块缺乏充分的权限验证机制，导致攻击者可获取服务器控制台完全访问权限，进而实现对整个系统的未授权控制。该漏洞影响 HP 800 S/X/V 系列服务器，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1163"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.297","remediation":"安装 HP 官方补丁 PF_CSXV1007（可从 HP Electronic Support Center FTP 获取），V22x0 系列升级 Teststation 至 5.1.2 版本，V2500 系列升级至 1.1.2 版本；同时应在网络边界限制对 SSP Teststation 服务的访问，仅允许受信任管理 IP 连接控制台端口。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94347039929958&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7439.php"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0989.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1004","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1189","title":"Netscape Navigator/Communicator 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Netscape Navigator/Communicator 4.7 for Windows 95/98 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向用户发送包含超长参数的恶意 URL（在 `?` 后附加超长参数，引用 .asp/.cgi/.html/.pl 文件），当浏览器解析该 URL 时触发缓冲区溢出，导致目标系统拒绝服务，甚至可能执行任意命令。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1189"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:54.500","remediation":"升级至 Netscape 4.72 或更高版本修复了该缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于 Netscape 已停止维护，建议立即停止使用该浏览器，改用 Firefox、Chrome 或 Edge 等仍在支持中的现代浏览器。如无法升级，可在代理服务器或网络边缘设备上过滤包含超长参数的特殊 URL 请求。Windows 95/98 系统本身已停止安全支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/36306","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/36608","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/822","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7884","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1189.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1189","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1189.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1189.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/057c97aa60eb958a2d272c7164e35c156db63b6c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f9rc-g2vv-h5f9/GHSA-f9rc-g2vv-h5f9.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ff933acb-86a6-4439-9da4-9b97189bec4f.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1189.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0638","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0638.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0844","title":"Deerfield MDaemon URL 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Deerfield MDaemon 2.8.5 及 2.8.6 版本（以及 Alt-N WorldClient Pro/Standard 2.0.0.x）的 Web 服务组件在处理超长 URL 请求时存在缓冲区处理缺陷，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向目标服务器发送特制长 URL 请求触发服务崩溃，导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 MDaemon 邮件服务器的 Web 管理界面与 WorldClient Webmail 组件，攻击复杂度低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0844"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-24","updated":"1999-11-24","remediation":"建议立即升级 MDaemon 至 2.8.7 或更高版本，该版本修复了 URL 处理中的缓冲区边界检查缺陷。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙层面限制对 WorldClient（端口 2000）和 WebConfig（端口 2002）的访问，仅允许受信任 IP 连接，或部署反向代理限制 URL 长度以临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19640"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0638.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0786","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0786.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0980","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Service Control Manager 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 服务控制管理器（SCM）在处理资源枚举请求时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送包含畸形参数的资源枚举请求触发 Services.exe 进程崩溃，导致系统服务拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 SP1 至 SP6 所有版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程发起攻击，仅需向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求即可触发 Services.exe 进程崩溃，导致系统服务停止响应，需重启系统恢复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0980"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-23","updated":"2026-07-14","remediation":"立即升级到 Windows NT 4.0 SP6a（MS99-055 安全公告）或更高版本；若已无法升级，建议迁移到 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本，同时在网络边界过滤 SMB/RPC 端口并关闭不必要的服务以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-055","http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb;%5BLN%5D;Q246045","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19578"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0786.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0911","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0911.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1058","title":"Vermillion FTP Daemon 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Vermillion FTP Daemon VFTPD 1.23 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务器发送多个特制的超长 CWD 命令触发该漏洞，导致服务进程崩溃引发拒绝服务，在特定条件下甚至可能执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 VFTPD 1.23 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，建议升级或限制访问以降低风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1058"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.050","remediation":"立即停止使用已停止维护的 Vermillion FTP Daemon VFTPD 1.23，迁移至现代活跃维护的 FTP 服务器（如 vsftpd 或 ProFTPD），或在条件允许时改用 SFTP/FTPS 替代 FTP 协议。如暂时无法迁移，应在网络边界防火墙限制对 FTP 端口（默认 21）的访问来源 IP，并使用 IPS/IDS 规则检测并阻断超长 CWD 命令（正常 CWD 路径长度通常不超过 256 字符）以缓解缓冲区溢出风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94329968617085&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94337185023159&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/818","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3543","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1058","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1058.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7cj6-wm7r-4g46/GHSA-7cj6-wm7r-4g46.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/V/vftpd_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/818/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0911.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0580","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0580.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0818","title":"Sun Solaris 7.0 kcms_configure NETPATH 环境变量缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 系统中的 kcms_configure 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置超长的 NETPATH 环境变量触发该漏洞，导致权限提升，获取 root 级别系统控制权。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 版本，攻击者需要本地 shell 权限即可利用，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0818"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.333","remediation":"从 Sun（甲骨文）获取并安装 Solaris 7 对应补丁（如 Patch ID 107081-xx 等 kcms_configure 相关补丁集）；若无法打补丁，立即移除 kcms_configure 的 setuid root 权限位（chmod u-s /usr/dt/bin/kcms_configure），该操作可阻断本地提权利用，或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本以彻底修复此缓冲区溢出漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/831","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=38433B7F5A.53F4SHADOWPENGUIN%40fox.nightland.net","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19647"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0580.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0580.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0580.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0617","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0617.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0831","title":"Linux Kernel Syslog 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux syslogd 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 syslog 服务发送大量网络连接请求，耗尽系统日志处理资源，导致 syslogd 崩溃或停止响应，无法正常记录日志。该漏洞影响多个 Linux 发行版本，攻击条件简单，无需身份认证即可实施攻击，危害等级中等。建议升级版本或限制网络访问以缓解风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0831"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:08.923","remediation":"升级 sysklogd 至 1.3 及以上版本（该版本修复了并发连接处理缺陷）；若使用 Caldera OpenLinux，安装 CSSA-1999-035.0 安全补丁。现代环境建议迁移至 rsyslog 或 syslog-ng 替代传统 syslogd，并在防火墙层面限制 UDP/TCP 514 端口的来源 IP 范围，仅允许受信日志发送端访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/809"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0617.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0832","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0832.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0999","title":"Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 TDS Packet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 在处理 TDS（Tabular Data Stream）协议数据包时存在输入验证不足漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器发送特制的空数据（NULL Data）TDS 报文，导致 SQL Server 服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 及 7.0 SP1 版本，CVSS 评分 4.3，危害等级中危。Microsoft 已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0999"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.610","remediation":"建议立即升级到 Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 Service Pack 2（SP2）或更高版本，该更新修复了 TDS 协议数据包畸形输入校验缺陷。如无法升级，可在网络边界防火墙配置规则过滤对 1433/TCP 端口的非授权访问，并限制可信来源 IP 以降低远程攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ248749","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/817","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-059","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19638","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0999.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0999.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0999","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0999.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0999.json","https://github.com/morpheuslord/CVE-llm_dataset/blob/91b337d05c623a68829de977c2b1ae6c0f91702b/README.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/mssqlserver_dos.nasl","https://github.com/dependency-check/DependencyCheck/blob/8119dd0f6e121ff60c6eaace2de1791c2a81c41d/core/src/main/resources/dependencycheck-base-suppression.xml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cj38-2rjc-pv2v/GHSA-cj38-2rjc-pv2v.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0832.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1124","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1124.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1475","title":"ProFTPD mod_sqlpw 密码泄露漏洞","description":"ProFTPD 1.2 在编译启用 mod_sqlpw 模块时存在敏感信息泄露漏洞。该模块会将用户认证密码明文记录到系统 wtmp 日志文件中，本地攻击者可通过执行 last 等命令读取 wtmp 日志获取其他用户的明文密码，进而利用获取的密码提升权限或横向移动。该漏洞影响 ProFTPD 1.2 版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，攻击复杂度低，CVSS v2 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1475"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-19","updated":"1999-11-19","remediation":"升级 ProFTPD 至 1.2.1 及以上版本，该版本已修复 mod_sqlpw 将用户密码明文写入 wtmp 日志的问题。如无法升级，可卸载 mod_sqlpw 模块或限制 wtmp 日志文件的读取权限（chmod 640 /var/log/wtmp），仅允许 root 用户访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1124.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1600","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1600.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0987","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 域认证机制存在安全缺陷，当域用户在登录时输入的域名末尾包含空格字符，系统无法正确下载并应用域安全策略，导致绕过身份认证。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，攻击者只需拥有域账户，通过在域名后附加空格即可触发。利用方式简单，危害等级严重，CVSS 评分 10.0。微软已发布安全更新修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0987"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.090","remediation":"建议立即升级 Windows NT 4.0 至 Service Pack 6a 或更高版本，该补丁（KB Q237923）修复了域登录时尾部空格导致策略下载失败的问题。对于无法升级的系统，应在登录流程入口处对域名字段做 Trim 处理，去除首尾空白字符，并确保域控制器和客户端统一校验域名格式。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ237923","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/3701042200a4e64b9e2a7f3614e9e958db6af9cd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0987","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0987.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1e5167f2-8c39-4729-bfeb-a8843e869244.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/fef2105ce9bc36a63673a5e0577e307a0953c8a8/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1600.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0528","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0528.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0793","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer JavaScript URL 重定向信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0.1 与 5.0 版本存在 JavaScript URL 重定向安全漏洞，源于浏览器对通过 JavaScript 小程序（applet）重定向数据的处理缺乏充分限制。远程攻击者可在网页中构造恶意 JavaScript 代码，诱导受害者访问特制页面后，将本应受同源策略保护的数据重定向并读取本地或跨域文件内容，从而泄露敏感信息。该漏洞影响运行上述版本 IE 的 Windows 系统，需用户在攻击者的诱导下访问恶意网页方可触发，攻击条件为远程、需用户交互，CVSS 基础评分 2.6，危害等级较低。Microsoft 已在安全公告 MS99-043 中提供相应修复。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0793"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-11-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:04.173","remediation":"升级至 Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.01 或更高版本并安装安全更新 MS99-043，或在 Internet 选项安全设置中禁用 JavaScript 执行作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-043","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19559","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0793.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c271719fd48dcc28619dc324e441b822d7b4bace/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0793.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0793","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0793.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0793.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/907ae4099f60f85a9473cd7e47129d370c445f83/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mj4p-5fc7-96gj/GHSA-mj4p-5fc7-96gj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0793.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0528.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0528.toml"}]